  "texts": [
    "ML models like Random Forest (RF) and Support Vector Machine (SVM) demonstrate strong classification capabilities but are challenged by issues like data imbalance and scalability in real-time applications.",
    "Ensemble methods and hybrid models that combine ML with other techniques show promise for improving accuracy.",
    "DL models, especially CNNs and LSTMs, excel in capturing complex patterns, making them suitable for high-dimensional data.",
    "However, they often demand substantial computational resources and are prone to overfitting with limited data, highlighting the need for efficient training techniques and model regularization.",
    "MHO algorithms, such as Genetic Algorithms and Particle Swarm Optimization, improve feature selection and model tuning, enhancing detection rates."
